data.description: Wow this beautiful move in ready 1315sqft ranch offers 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, cathedral ceilings, recessed lighting throughout, Hardwood Floors, and 1st floor laundry. The kitchen's doorwall opens onto a deck, extending the living space outdoors. The large fenced yard is perfect for outdoor gatherings and summer night bonfires. The extra deep partially finished basement has 10ft ceilings, offers 4th bedroom and  lots of open living space and storage space. Heated 2 car attached garage. Pride of ownership shows, you will not be disappointed! Nestled in a sought-after neighborhood within the Lanse Creuse School District, with parks nearby and easy access to the highway, this home offers both comfort and convenience in equal measure.
